title: The transsexual Wisconsin students were forced to wear green bracelets?
subtitle: According to social media rumours, transsexual students in Wisconsin were forced to wear green bracelets, bracelets or bracelets to identify them and monitor their use of the bathroom.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: Students in Wisconsin are forced to wear armbands, bracelets or pink triangles to define them as transsexuals.
